// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0173 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 99964758-3adb-5c7b-99cb-444619766dab

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*azure linux:3.0*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*")
